    dc:creator "Hansen, Jesper G.; Kristensen, Reinhardt M." ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "A new genus and five new species of the subfamily Florarctinae (Tardigrada, Arthrotardigrada)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211789>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211791>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211795>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211819>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211823> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211789>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. General features of the lateral alae of Higginsarctus gen. nov. The procuticle sends out branches (ramuli) to the edge of the alae. Drawing by Stine B. Elle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5211789/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211791>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Higginsarctus signeae gen. et sp. nov. Ventral overview. Holotype, ♀ (NHMD-293899). Abbreviations: see Material and methods. Drawing by Stine B. Elle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5211791/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211795>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. SEM-micrographs of Higginsarctus signeae gen. et sp. nov., paratype, ♀ (NHMD-293902). A. Ventro-lateral overview. B. Close up on the head, lateral view showing cephalic cirri and secondary clava. C. Internal cirrus. D. External cirrus. E. Gonopore and genital stoup. F–G. Scapus of cirrus E broken in two (note the unique small papillae of scapus). H. Primary clavae (broken) and lateral cirrus. Abbreviations: see Material and methods." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5211795/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211819>
    dc:description "Fig. 14. Higginsarctus laurae gen. et sp. nov., holotype, ♀ (NHMD-293905). Ventral overview. Abbreviations: see Material and methods. Drawing by Stine B. Elle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5211819/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5211823>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. DIC-micrographs of Higginsarctus laurae gen. et sp. nov. A. Paratype, ♀ (NHMD-293907). Overview. B–D. Paratype, ♀ (NHMD-293908). B. Close up on the head, ventral view showing the external cirri and secondary clavae. C. Close up on the caudal region, ventral view showing the folia and gonopore. D. Close up on the bucco-pharyngeal apparatus. Abbreviations: see Material and methods." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5211823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

